                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/1187</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from"
                            >Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-05-07T12:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 7, 1916, noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>46. Department’s 70, May 6, 6 p.m. Mining law effective May 1, practically same
                    as that transmitted with mail despatch 25. Minor modifications only.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
